      <title>美联储降息之路畅通，国债市场迎来转折点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/treasury-market-hits-a-turning-point-as-path-clears-for-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的债券市场正在迎来一个转折点，随着交易员开始接受今年三次降息的想法，美国国债将抹去 2024 年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/treasury-market-hits-a-turning-point-as-path-clears-for-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 15:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Kaszek 和 Andreessen 为阿根廷金融科技公司 Tapi 提供 2200 万美元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/argentina-fintech-tapi-raises-22-million-from-kaszek-andreessen-horowitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷金融科技初创公司 Tapi 联合创始人兼首席执行官托马斯·明德林 (Tomas Mindlin) 表示，该公司正在扩大其在墨西哥的业务，在由 Kaszek 领投的 A 轮融资中筹集了 2200 万美元的风险投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/argentina-fintech-tapi-raises-22-million-from-kaszek-andreessen-horowitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果首次通过合资企业提供钴资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/congo-offers-own-cobalt-from-joint-ventures-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国的国有矿业公司正试图出售其在合资项目中持有的钴股份，以寻求对能源转型至关重要的金属的更多控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/congo-offers-own-cobalt-from-joint-ventures-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗新任银行主管获得 4100 万美元股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/citi-s-new-banking-chief-gets-41-million-in-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团今年早些时候聘请 Viswas Raghavan 担任其新银行业务主管，并已向高管授予了价值约 4100 万美元的股份（按当前价值计算）。Sonali Basak 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/citi-s-new-banking-chief-gets-41-million-in-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员开始押注美联储 9 月份大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/traders-start-to-bet-on-a-supersized-fed-rate-cut-in-september</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员正在加大对美联储 9 月份降息半个百分点而非标准的四分之一个百分点的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/traders-start-to-bet-on-a-supersized-fed-rate-cut-in-september</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行计划为赛诺菲消费品业务出售提供 60 亿欧元债务融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/banks-plan-6-billion-debt-financing-for-sanofi-consumer-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，包括高盛集团和摩根士丹利在内的多家银行正在为赛诺菲消费者健康部门的潜在买家提供超过 60 亿欧元（65 亿美元）的债务融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/banks-plan-6-billion-debt-financing-for-sanofi-consumer-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于建筑成本上升，ADM 放弃与 LG 化学的合资项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/adm-scraps-ventures-with-lg-chem-as-construction-costs-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于成本过高，农业巨头阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司已停止与 LG 化学有限公司的合资生产生物塑料等植物产品的材料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/adm-scraps-ventures-with-lg-chem-as-construction-costs-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:29:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑多头享受工党胜利 降息预期推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/pound-euphoria-builds-with-5-billion-riding-on-further-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英镑目前处于多年来的最高水平，巩固了其在 G-10 货币中的领先地位，高盛集团和百达集团的策略师预测英镑未来将进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/pound-euphoria-builds-with-5-billion-riding-on-further-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价连续第三天上涨，因时间推移表明需求强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关键市场指标显示出需求增强的迹象且交易员评估利率前景，油价连续第三天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 23:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
